  "title": "PROJECT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<p>· Degree in Civil Engineering (Recognized Degree by PE Board)</p>\n<p>· Min 5 years relevant working experience in Civil Construction Works</p>\n<p>· Dynamic, self-motivated, proactive, and results-oriented with a proven track record in the Civil Engineering industry</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>• Reporting to Managing Director</p>\n<p>• Responsible for overall project planning, scheduling, monitoring and updating to meet targets</p>\n<p>• Lead a team of professional &amp; technical trained staff in planning, daily operations liaise with clients, consultants, sub-contractors &amp; relevant authorities</p>\n<p>• Manage the Project for the following</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Design</li>\n  <li>Construction</li>\n  <li>Safety</li>\n  <li>Coordination with Client</li>\n  <li>Planning &amp; Scheduling</li>\n</ul>",
